                " Ge(Li) detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Isomer ratios determined as average of 4 experiments:",
                ". two from 117In 314-keV vs 554-keV gammas:",
                "  samples counted 1 hr, 40 mins after irradiation",
                "  and 2 hrs, 39 mins after irradiation.",
                ". one from 117In 554-keV gamma, 2 successive",
                "  countings 9 hrs, 24 mins after irradiation and",
                "  11 hrs, 21 mins after irradiation.",
                ". one from 117Cd spectra counted 5 hrs, 50 mins after",
                "  irradiation for 59 mins."
              ]
            }
          ],
